{"tid":2268980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場姐姐： 查閱車主資料作報導用途最高可判監禁六個月","createTime":"2020-11-03T07:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T08:13:09.000Z","uid":22556,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2505b3c8c5730111269ebdd69f09fa25a6c7bf7d","tid":2268980,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"若傳媒消息屬實，港台編導蔡玉玲是因為，被指違反《道路安全條例》第111條第（3）款規定，可被判罰款5,000元，以及監禁六個月。<br />\n<br />\n查車牌原是傳媒進行偵查報道的重要工具，警隊亟欲封鎖禁絕。今年8月警察就曾拘捕一名查牌後公開資料的51歲男子，控罪是個人資料（私隱）條例下的「披露未經資料使用者同意而取得個人資料」罪。散仔協會舊年在司法覆核禁查選民登記冊後，就傳出有意再借警員被「起底」為由，要求限制公眾查車牌，循司法途徑申請禁制。<br />\n<br />\n事實證明，警察所關注的，遠遠不止警員是否被起底，這不過是個藉口而已。他們真正的目的，是要借勢將所有公開資料的渠道全部封殺，令第四權失卻監察公權的臂膀。<br />\n<br />\n721 果然是香港警謊最不能招架的痛點。不等法庭，他們自己就先出手了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104809544486282/posts/195187125448523/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104809544486282%2Fposts%2F195187125448523%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=5dcfaff4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104809544486282/posts/195187125448523/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"b3e4dcc4f95eddca5b76be2f8c38295d655dede4","tid":2268980,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T07:46:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51abb36776136af25590e29cac1c85f666ad1d99","tid":2268980,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T07:47:00.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks"},{"pid":"aba4c372007fc052e875fb73458904ca40e46fa8","tid":2268980,"uid":321059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T07:47:17.000Z","msg":"黑警 你拉得港台記者 麻煩你拉埋呢位大公報記者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2268969\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2268969</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98410e972fad569d309efb2fbed2d3381dee9fc","tid":2268980,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aba4c372007fc052e875fb73458904ca40e46fa8","tid":2268980,"uid":321059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T07:47:17.000Z","msg":"黑警 你拉得港台記者 麻煩你拉埋呢位大公報記者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2268969\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2268969</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:13:09.000Z","msg":"If we burn<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}